### 6.4 Features

| Feature             | ars-ui                     | React Aria |
| ------------------- | -------------------------- | ---------- |
| Keyboard navigation | Yes                        | Yes        |
| Overflow to menu    | Yes                        | Yes        |
| Selection modes     | Yes (None/Single/Multiple) | Yes        |
| RTL support         | Yes                        | Yes        |
| Roving tabindex     | Yes                        | Yes        |

**Gaps:** None.

